<br>
Yes lots of people will quit coming here, but lots will start coming back because there will be good disucssions and information to improve the game for eveyone, rather than this board turning into whineplay and flame wars.<br>
<br>
Im not against disagreements or heated discussions, just keep them on a professional level.  <br>
<br>
